description: Happy Tuesday! Here is a bonus shoot for you to enjoy mid-week. This update was shot almost 2 years ago on location in Tahoe. Annie Cruz gets in trouble for falling asleep while she's supposed to be watching Harmony, so Princess Donna, Ariel X, and Harmony gang up on her. When the leg of the coffee table gets broken on accident we stuff it right up Annie's ass and make her squirt and cum uncontrollably!Since this is an old shoot it does not reflect our current shooting and encoding standards. But don't worry you can look forward to one of our super high quality HD shoots on Thursday. This is only a BONUS!!
title: Ariel X, Harmony and Annie Cruz
